00039 MTKt_status MtkTimeMetaRead(
00040   const char *filename, 
00041   MTKt_TimeMetaData *time_metadata  )
00042 {
00043   MTKt_status status;      /* Return status */
00044   MTKt_status status_code; /* Return code of this function */
00045   int32 hdf_status;        /* HDF-EOS return status */
00046   int32 sd_id = FAIL;      /* HDF SD file identifier. */
00047   int32 hdf_id = FAIL;
00048   
00049   if (filename == NULL)
00050     MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_NULLPTR);
00051 
00052   /* Open HDF File */
00053   hdf_id = HDFopen(filename, DFACC_READ, 0);
00054   if (hdf_id == FAIL)
00055     MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_HDF_HDFOPEN_FAILED);
00056 
00057   /* Open HDF File */
00058   hdf_status = sd_id = SDstart(filename, DFACC_READ);
00059   if (hdf_status == FAIL)
00060     MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_HDF_SDSTART_FAILED);
00061 
00062   /* Read time metadata. */
00063   status = MtkTimeMetaReadFid(hdf_id, sd_id, time_metadata);
00064   MTK_ERR_COND_JUMP(status);
00065     
00066   /* Close HDF File */
00067   hdf_status = SDend(sd_id);
00068   if (hdf_status == FAIL)
00069     MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_HDF_SDEND_FAILED);
00070   sd_id = FAIL;
00071    
00072   /* Close HDF file */
00073   hdf_status = HDFclose(hdf_id);
00074   if (hdf_status == FAIL)
00075     MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_HDF_HDFCLOSE_FAILED);
00076   hdf_id = FAIL;
00077 
00078   return MTK_SUCCESS;
00079  
00080 ERROR_HANDLE:
00081   if (hdf_id != FAIL)
00082     HDFclose(hdf_id);
00083   
00084   if (sd_id != FAIL)
00085     SDend(sd_id);
00086 
00087   return status_code;
00088 }

00095 MTKt_status MtkTimeMetaReadFid(

00101   MTKt_status status_code; /* Return code of this function */

00103   int i;

00114   if (time_metadata == NULL)
00115     MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_NULLPTR);
00116     
00117   /* Read block metadata */

00119                     "number_transform", &number_transform);
00120   MTK_ERR_COND_JUMP(status);

00122   status = MtkFileBlockMetaFieldReadFid(hdf_id, "PerBlockMetadataRad",
00123                     "transform.ref_time", &ref_time);
00124   MTK_ERR_COND_JUMP(status);

00126   status = MtkFileBlockMetaFieldReadFid(hdf_id, "PerBlockMetadataRad",

00150                                &time_metadata->end_block);      
00151   MTK_ERR_COND_JUMP(status);

00153   status = MtkFileAttrGetFid(sd_id, "Camera", &camera);
00154   MTK_ERR_COND_JUMP(status);
00155 
00156   strcpy(time_metadata->camera, cam_list[camera.data.i32[0][0] - 1]);
00157 
00158   /* Block is 0-based when read from Per Block Metadata convert
00159      to 1-based when copying to Time Metadata structure */
00160      
00161   memcpy(time_metadata->number_transform + 1, number_transform.dataptr,
00162          sizeof(MTKt_int32) * number_transform.nline);
00163          
00164   for (block = 0; block < ref_time.nline; ++block)
00165   {
00166     /* ref_time is stored as two strings concatenated together, split
00167        when copying into Time Metadata structure */
00168     
00169     strncpy(time_metadata->ref_time[block + 1][0], ref_time.data.c8[block],
00170             MTKd_DATETIME_LEN - 1);
00171     time_metadata->ref_time[block + 1][0][MTKd_DATETIME_LEN - 1] = '\0';
00172 
00173     strncpy(time_metadata->ref_time[block + 1][1], ref_time.data.c8[block] + MTKd_DATETIME_LEN - 1,
00174             MTKd_DATETIME_LEN - 1);
00175     time_metadata->ref_time[block + 1][1][MTKd_DATETIME_LEN - 1] = '\0';
00176   }
00177   
00178   memcpy(time_metadata->start_line + 1, start_line.dataptr,
00179          sizeof(MTKt_int32) * start_line.nline * start_line.nsample);
00180   
00181   memcpy(time_metadata->number_line + 1, number_line.dataptr,
00182          sizeof(MTKt_int32) * number_line.nline * number_line.nsample);
00183   
00184   for (block = 0; block < coeff_line.nline; ++block)
00185     for (i = 0; i < 6; ++i)
00186     {
00187       /* reorder coeff_line by grid cell */
00188       time_metadata->coeff_line[block + 1][i][0] = coeff_line.data.d[block][i];
00189       time_metadata->coeff_line[block + 1][i][1] = coeff_line.data.d[block][i + 6];
00190     }
00191   
00192   memcpy(time_metadata->som_ctr_x + 1, som_ctr_x.dataptr,
00193          sizeof(MTKt_double) * som_ctr_x.nline * som_ctr_x.nsample);
00194   
00195   memcpy(time_metadata->som_ctr_y + 1, som_ctr_y.dataptr,
00196          sizeof(MTKt_double) * som_ctr_y.nline * som_ctr_y.nsample);
00197   
00198   MtkDataBufferFree(&number_transform);
00199   MtkDataBufferFree(&ref_time);
00200   MtkDataBufferFree(&start_line);
00201   MtkDataBufferFree(&number_line);

00207   return MTK_SUCCESS;
00208  
00209 ERROR_HANDLE:
00210   MtkDataBufferFree(&number_transform);
00211   MtkDataBufferFree(&ref_time);
